07. Favorite Band
# Congrats!
<h2>Woohoo! (╥﹏╥)</h2>
<p>You've reached the end of chapter 1 🫶</p>

Here's a refresher on what we went over:

HTML elements, tags, and indentation.
Heading tags: <h1> - <h6>.
Paragraph and line breaks: <p>, <br>.
Text formatting: <b>, <i>, <u>, <s>.
Unordered and ordered lists: <ul>, <ol>.
Links and images: <a>, <img>.
Let's put everything together!

Instructions
Create a band.html page for your favorite artist using all the elements we learned and at least two types of text formatting.



It should include the following:

The name of the artist.
A picture of the artist or album cover.
A short blurb about the artist.
A link to the artist's website.
The members in an unordered list.
Top 5 favorite songs in an ordered list.
When it's done, take a screenshot and click the Twitter icon to post your band page! 🎸



----code-----
<!-- Write code below 💖 -->

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Favorite Artist</title>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- Artist Name -->
  <h1>Imagine Dragons</h1>

  <!-- Artist Image -->
  <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/3/3f/Imagine_Dragons_2013.jpg" 
       alt="Imagine Dragons Band" width="300">

  <!-- Description -->
  <h2>About the Artist</h2>
  <p>
    Imagine Dragons is an American pop rock band known for their energetic music and hit songs like 
    "Believer" and "Radioactive". Their music blends rock, pop, and electronic elements.
  </p>

  <!-- Website Link -->
  <h2>Official Website</h2>
  <p>
    Visit their website:
    <a href="https://www.imaginedragonsmusic.com" target="_blank">
      Imagine Dragons Official Site
    </a>
  </p>

  <!-- Members -->
  <h2>Band Members</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Dan Reynolds</li>
    <li>Wayne Sermon</li>
    <li>Ben McKee</li>
    <li>Daniel Platzman</li>
  </ul>

  <!-- Top 5 Songs -->
  <h2>Top 5 Favorite Songs</h2>
  <ol>
    <li>Believer</li>
    <li>Radioactive</li>
    <li>Demons</li>
    <li>Thunder</li>
    <li>Whatever It Takes</li>
  </ol>

</body>
</html>
